author: Nexcell Pride
text:
A memorable stream... With a challenge inside... Diamonds and excavation in 60 minutes. :_ちょうちょ:
But Rushia-hime went too far, not only beaten Taizo Hori and his son Susumu Hori from "Dig Dug" and "Mr. Driller" franchises Record excavation... :_くさｗ: Also in 1 hour, and at least the minimal arsenal, she got 84 Diamonds and 9 Emeralds, ideal for too much Bridal Proposals... :_るんるん: (Sweating in that September's Morning stream with the breakfast) That surpassed the 50 Diamond challenge at September stream. (I can't remember well if were 50 or 60, but I remember, 10 diamonds are given to Aqua-san) 

And we are wondering... What will Rushia-hime do with all those gems? 

At Supaachaato Orei Time, again Superchats went boom, but also went boom at mission accomplished. :_なのです::_サイリウム碧::_サイリウム紫:

And personally talking... Problem solved about the superchat I sent her at yesterday's stream... :_ハート::_きゅん:

Again Rushia-hime demonstrated she is more closer to fans inside and outside fandeads membership.

author: Amai Ta. Yume
text:
Thank you for the stream fandeads and Rushia-san! I had a lot of fun! Congrats on the Diamond hunt. It was very very worth it! <3 <3

るしあストリームありがとうございます！ <3 楽しかった！ダイヤモンドハントおめでとうございます。とても貴重でした！


また、ENブラザーズとJPブラザーズのルシアへのサポートにも感謝します！
